hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好sweet咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢有呢份心意係幾好嘅<br />\n不過都冇整過都dum埋咗一二邊</blockquote><br />\n起碼我冇收過以前男朋友親手整d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好少親手整野比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整嚟整去都好老套<br />\n又係相簿同生日卡"},{"pid":"f18316a00998c1c8978b1cd2bdd31b00de8da72b","tid":374204,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"幾件佢覺得靚既柒衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3042573c467e95ce0f03f23ceb02cb6528db7d7","tid":374204,"uid":68987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"潛力po留名"},{"pid":"e4f76e6a49677d01dc3fa327afc1f14d679418f5","tid":374204,"uid":54597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"雜誌紙包住六包濕紙巾"},{"pid":"d429482d5aee689f615a6b015bf43fec00bd9728","tid":374204,"uid":46472,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"試過拍拖2個月果陣，啱啱到我生日前一晚傾電話，仲同佢講好期待佢送嘅禮物，佢話「吓，我冇買禮物啊」，以為佢諗住俾個驚喜我，<br />\n點知佢真係冇買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 卡都唔寫一張俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢見我雖然冇發佢脾氣，但睇落都好失望，<br />\n過咗排佢番大陸探親嘅時候順便買咗個山寨版史奴比勁細隻嘅公仔俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有之後喺情人節又送咗條大陸螢光綠色嘅吊飾俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：已散"},{"pid":"04c04c53de52129ab69d4c99119b759d46c717eb","tid":374204,"uid":49642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"依家太陽油都200蚊支架樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa59d674299178d2fd70ca532d7503f07a8b1873","tid":374204,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"